<br>
Also Lady Voxx was taken down approx 3 and a half hours later.  Clan Twisted hosted this event and what can I say it was invigorating. /smile.  Within 20 mins the only thing left in Vox's lair was a Terror and 1 Giant.  It was too much fun.  Average pull consisting of 3 giants.  Sounds crazy but not many deaths at all.  Lady Vox died a horrible death around 8:30 est.<br>
<br>
Medite and Tarin you lead very good raids.  I would be happy to be within your company whenever needed.<br>
